name: AnRKey X
short_description: AnRKey X™ combines DeFi and Esports gaming for users to compete, purchase and stake unique NFTs and win valuable rewards
description: Forked from Ethereum with Pulsechain. AnRKey X™ combines DeFi and Esports gaming for users to compete, purchase and stake unique NFTs and win valuable rewards. We are the first to attach a proprietary and underlying economic mathematical logic model to NFTs in order to derive a true and accurate monetary base value ($) in real time – which we call Derived Base Value
